'''煮食爐'''或称'''炉子'''、'''炉'''，是一種用來[[烹飪|烹飪]]的廚具，通過[[熱傳導|加熱]][[炊具|炊具]]來達到將食物變熟的目的，由於傳統的煮食爐是固定式的[[爐灶|爐灶]]，現在有時也會把一些煮食爐稱為「爐灶」、「灶」等。有[[火爐|火爐]]等使用[[火|火]]來加熱的煮食爐，也有[[電磁爐|電磁爐]]這樣的用[[電|電]]加熱的煮食爐。

==歷史==
===早期===
{{main|灶}}
[[File:Indonesian_brick_stove.jpg|thumb]]

早期的煮食爐是[[粘土|粘土]]、[[石材|石材]]、[[磚頭|磚頭]]等製作的，用最原始的火來加熱，稱為[[灶|灶]]。中國在春秋戰國已經有[[灶君|灶君]]出現，[[孔子|孔子]]就有“与其媚于奥，宁媚于灶”之說。[[古希臘|古希臘]]時也有用來烤麵包的火灶。<ref name="Bellis">{{cite web|url=http://inventors.about.com/od/ofamousinventions/a/oven.htm|title=History of the Oven from Cast Iron to Electric|author=Mary Bellis|accessdate=2015-03-06}}</ref> 中國和[[中世紀|中世紀]]的歐洲很早之前就使用磚砌、石製的爐灶來做飯。<ref name=Larousse>Montagne, Prosper ''New Larousse Gastronomique'' Hamlin Publishing Group 1977 </ref>

===近代的煮食爐===
[[File:Noć_muzeja_2015,_Čakovec_-_stari_štednjak_iz_19.st.jpg|thumb]][[梅吉慕捷郡博物館|梅吉慕捷郡博物館]]中的19世紀[[布達佩斯|布達佩斯]]製]]
[[File:Suzhou_woman_burning_waste_20090926_5964.jpg|缩略图]]街头，一位使用[[葵扇|芭蕉扇]]助燃[[蜂窝煤|蜂窝煤]]煤炉女性，另一手则持有拿取蜂窝煤的[[钳子|钳子]]。]]
1800年左右[[本傑明·湯普森，倫福德伯爵|本傑明·湯普森]]發明了[[鑄鐵|鑄鐵]]的煮食爐，即倫福德爐（Rumford stove），這算得上是現代煮食爐的雛形。<ref name="Bellis"/> 他也曾設計過磚制煮食爐。<ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=C7kuAgAAQBAJ|title=Clay: The History and Evolution of Humankind's Relationship with Earth's Most Primal Element|author=Suzanne Staubach|year=2013|publisher=UPNE|access-date=2015-03-06|archive-date=2017-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170117083801/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=C7kuAgAAQBAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>

也就是在19世紀初的歐洲，鑄鐵的煮食爐取代了石頭灶。1850年代，現代化的、專門配有煮食爐的廚房在中產階級家庭中流行開來。1850年代美國女性瑪麗·艾伐（Mary Evard）發明了一種煮食爐，還在1868年註冊了專利<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache%3Ac_PWfH8OlPYJ%3Avirtual.clemson.edu%2Fcaah%2Fwomen%2Fws301%2Fppt%2Fwoinvent%2FWomen%2520Inventors.ppt+%22mary+evard%22+stove&hl=en&gl=us&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEESivvRoz1udHC8Sa1Dxgd9ZHsKJLE6IJMiIUbaA0mQvbv_HbvaBsZXS7AP9ogqdG7Aaf9glEfBZ0oARYqhwEFuyR2tSGpe5K3uAmM3ZzFJAOqs2xYez0-phE2RS6CMzdXydpBZdR&sig=AHIEtbRbK9UP6EADgu2Nnavdg2O2JrYr5g |title=Google Drive Viewer<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2022-01-13 |archive-date=2019-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190813084248/https://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache%3Ac_PWfH8OlPYJ%3Avirtual.clemson.edu%2Fcaah%2Fwomen%2Fws301%2Fppt%2Fwoinvent%2FWomen%2520Inventors.ppt+%22mary+evard%22+stove&hl=en&gl=us&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEESivvRoz1udHC8Sa1Dxgd9ZHsKJLE6IJMiIUbaA0mQvbv_HbvaBsZXS7AP9ogqdG7Aaf9glEfBZ0oARYqhwEFuyR2tSGpe5K3uAmM3ZzFJAOqs2xYez0-phE2RS6CMzdXydpBZdR&sig=AHIEtbRbK9UP6EADgu2Nnavdg2O2JrYr5g |dead-url=no }}</ref> US76315和US76314，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.google.com/patents/US76315?pg=PA1&dq=evard&hl=en&sa=X&ei=j5rXUtK1A-qvsATAmoDYAQ&ved=0CEEQ6AEwAg |title=Patent US76315 - evard - Google Patents<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2015-03-06 |archive-date=2016-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161026094923/https://www.google.com/patents/US76315?pg=PA1&dq=evard&hl=en&sa=X&ei=j5rXUtK1A-qvsATAmoDYAQ&ved=0CEEQ6AEwAg |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.google.com/patents/US76314?dq=US76314&hl=en&sa=X&ei=WpzXUuGQEpStsQSpmoC4DQ&ved=0CDcQ6AEwAA |title=Patent US76314 - Improvement in broiling-apparatus - Google Patents<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2015-03-06 |archive-date=2016-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161026094921/https://www.google.com/patents/US76314?dq=US76314&hl=en&sa=X&ei=WpzXUuGQEpStsQSpmoC4DQ&ved=0CDcQ6AEwAA |dead-url=no }}</ref> 並在[[聖路易斯世界博覽會|聖路易斯世界博覽會]]上展出。<ref name="books.google.com">{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=D7IhN7lempUC&pg=PA958&lpg=PA958&dq=%22mary+evard%22+stove&source=bl&ots=HFaxW-Ecy-&sig=x6BqPNtiplgoyAr9StuOgOrzqfY&hl=en&sa=X&ei=Z9TPT8ugMeau6AH90fi1DA&ved=0CF8Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22mary%20evard%22%20stove&f=false |title=Ency Kitchen History - Google Books<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2015-03-06 |archive-date=2014-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110005955/http://books.google.com/books?id=D7IhN7lempUC&pg=PA958&lpg=PA958&dq=%22mary+evard%22+stove&source=bl&ots=HFaxW-Ecy-&sig=x6BqPNtiplgoyAr9StuOgOrzqfY&hl=en&sa=X&ei=Z9TPT8ugMeau6AH90fi1DA&ved=0CF8Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22mary%20evard%22%20stove&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref> 1867年紐約的伊麗莎白·霍克斯（Elizabeth Hawks）發明了附帶烤箱的煮食爐，<ref name="books.google.com"/> 也獲得了很大的成功。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=3vVYGAUjnEkC&pg=PT75&dq=%22elizabeth+hawks%22+two+thousand&hl=en&ei=ZQXQT8KvIeXe0QHu67ixDQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=book-thumbnail&resnum=1&ved=0CD4Q6wEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22elizabeth%20hawks%22%20two%20thousand&f=false |title=Feminine Ingenuity: How Women Inventors Changed America - Anne Macdonald - Google Books<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2015-03-06 |archive-date=2014-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021003110/http://books.google.com/books?id=3vVYGAUjnEkC&pg=PT75&dq=%22elizabeth+hawks%22+two+thousand&hl=en&ei=ZQXQT8KvIeXe0QHu67ixDQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=book-thumbnail&resnum=1&ved=0CD4Q6wEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22elizabeth%20hawks%22%20two%20thousand&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=rGkKO1C7hAYC&pg=PA52&dq=%22auxiliary+air+chamber+for+stoves%22&hl=en&ei=JAbQT5TpNcbc0QGD--3FDQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=book-thumbnail&resnum=9&ved=0CIMBEOsBMAg#v=onepage&q=%22auxiliary%20air%20chamber%20for%20stoves%22&f=false |title=Professional Pursuits: Women and the American Arts and Crafts Movement - Catherine W. Zipf - Google Books<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2015-03-06 |archive-date=2014-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140626071720/http://books.google.com/books?id=rGkKO1C7hAYC&pg=PA52&dq=%22auxiliary+air+chamber+for+stoves%22&hl=en&ei=JAbQT5TpNcbc0QGD--3FDQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=book-thumbnail&resnum=9&ved=0CIMBEOsBMAg#v=onepage&q=%22auxiliary%20air%20chamber%20for%20stoves%22&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>

配合煤炉，日本发明的[[蜂窝煤|蜂窝煤]]成为20世纪[[东亚|东亚]]居民普遍使用的家用烹饪、取暖燃料。

===天然氣和電加熱的煮食爐===
{{main|瓦斯爐|電煮食爐}}
[[File:Electric_stove.jpg|thumb]]
19世紀的煮食爐大多數仍然使用煤炭或木頭來點火，<ref>[http://www.rangehoodsstore.com/articles/2010/04/the-history-of-kitchen-appliances/ The History of Kitchen Appliances] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100616233144/http://www.rangehoodsstore.com/articles/2010/04/the-history-of-kitchen-appliances/ |date=2010-06-16 }}</ref> 但1820年代第一個天然氣煮食爐就已經出現了。1826年英格蘭[[北安普頓|北安普頓]]的詹姆斯·夏普（James Sharp）註冊了一個天然氣煮食爐專利，1828年後他的專利就由史密斯和菲利普斯（Smith & Philips）公司市場化 ，1836年開啟了最早的天然氣灶工廠。法國廚師[[亞歷克西斯·索亞|亞歷克西斯·索亞]]在1841年開始給自己的煮食爐接入天然氣管道。<ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=SJGNAgAAQBAJ|title=Encyclopedia of Kitchen History|author=Mary Ellen Snodgrass|year=2004|publisher=Routledge|page=428|access-date=2015-03-06|archive-date=2017-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171001213621/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=SJGNAgAAQBAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>  

在[[電氣|電氣]]時代來臨之後，電力很快就成為了煮食爐的熱力來源。加拿大發明家[[托馬斯·埃亨|托馬斯·埃亨]]在1892年成為了最早將電氣煮食爐專利化的人。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/innovations/023020-2460-e.html |title=Patent no. 39916 |work=Made in Canada |publisher=Library and Archives Canada |date=November 22, 2005 |accessdate=October 19, 2011 |archive-date=2018-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180116004735/http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/innovations/023020-2460-e.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sciencetech.technomuses.ca/english/collection/stoves5.cfm |title=Early Electric Cooking: 1900 to 1920 |publisher=Canada Science and Technology Museum |accessdate=October 19, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014004436/http://www.sciencetech.technomuses.ca/english/collection/stoves5.cfm |archive-date=2014-10-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 1893年的[[芝加哥世界博覽會|芝加哥世界博覽會]]上這種電氣灶曾參展。

但電氣煮食爐的普及因電力供應問題而一直難以普及，<ref name="Sobey10">Ed Sobey, ''The Way Kitchens Work'', Chicago Review Press, 2010 ISBN 1569762813,  page viii</ref> 1905年11月29日大衛·科爾·史密斯為他設計的電氣灶申請了澳大利亞專利No. 4699/05，這是最早的實用型電氣灶之一。<ref>Introduction by [[H._A._Willis|H. A. Willis]], ''Thermo-Electrical Cooking Made Easy'', Hesperian Press, 2011, ISBN 978-0-85905-492-8 p. 24</ref>

[[電磁爐|電磁爐]]的發明也要追溯到1900年代初，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://appliancehelp.com/Frigidaire-Cooktop-Parts.htm |title=Induction Cooktops |publisher=Appliance Help |accessdate=2013-05-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515165619/http://appliancehelp.com/Frigidaire-Cooktop-Parts.htm |archivedate=2013-05-15 }}</ref> 當時也出現了第一個電磁爐專利。<ref>for example see UK Patent Application GB190612333, entitled "Improvements in or relating to Apparatus for the Electrical Production of Heat for Cooking and other purposes", applied for by Arthur F. Berry on 26 May 1906</ref> 1950年代[[通用汽車|通用汽車]]的子公司[[富及第|富及第]]在北美洲巡迴展出了他們設計的電磁爐，<ref>''Kitchen of the Future has Glass-Dome Oven and Automatic Food Mixer'', Popular Mechanics Apr 1956, page 88</ref> 當時的宣傳是在電磁爐與鍋之間放了一張報紙，以報紙沒有被點燃來顯示其安全性。1970年代[[西屋公司|西屋公司]]發明電磁爐也很大程度上影響了這種電器的推廣。<ref name=Moreland73>W. C.Moreland, ''The Induction Range: Its Performance and Its Development Problems'', IEEE Transactions on Industry Applications, vol. TA-9, no. 1, January/February 1973 pages 81–86</ref>

